### REST Client requests for Python AI Service
# Requires VS Code REST Client extension or any compatible HTTP runner
# Set the base URL for your running FastAPI server
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check (optional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### Intent classification example
POST {{baseUrl}}/intent/classify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "tư vấn cách chăm sóc cà chua mùa mưa",
  "top_k": 3
}

### NER extraction - crop example
POST {{baseUrl}}/ner/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "cách trồng cà chua tại ruộng số 5 ngày mai"
}

